description: Here lies the ordinal quintet, not being actual difficulties, but rather obstacle courses, the final challenge before The Final Difficulty. Each ordinal represents an endlessly unbeatable barrier you must overcome, though none can truly compare to the finale. Rating estimates were given, but these ordinals are infinite, albeit not in the same sense or timeline as TFinD. However, they serve to prepare the player for what may inevitably be the end of the difficulty chart.
